  "texts": [
    "Among the 45 students of Grade 10 in Ipil National High School, only 30 percent of the class could construct an outstanding essay and the rest rely on the help of the knowledgeable others.",
    "More often they tend to plagiarized written works found online just to comply with the activities given by their teacher.",
    "Generally, there is a poor performance of learners in their writing skill.",
    "With the use of technology, learners could instantly come up with good essays by just merely typing the topic.",
    "The most common tool used by students nowadays is the Generative AI."
  ]
}